## Github Action version verification

Check what is the most up-to-date version of certain Github Actions with the following command:

```bash
curl -s https://api.github.com/repos/{owner}/{repo}/releases/latest | grep '"tag_name":' | sed -E 's/.*"v([0-9]+).*/\1/'
```